<h3>Description</h3>
<p>Tests whether a file exists or not before compiling starts. If the required file is
missing, an error error is raised with the custom message.
</p>The base directory for the file check is the project directory

<h3>Example</h3>
<code>
    // Make sure that "myData.bin" is created before compile
    @requirefile "data/myData.bin"  "Please run the data file generator 'mydata_generator.fjo' before compiling this file."
</code>
